Developer Terms of Use
des:
Can you spot the differences before time runs out?

Test your observation skills with ten fun and colorful levels. If you're fast enough, you'll earn all thirty stars, but if you make too many mistakes, you'll have to start over!

Spot the Difference is only supported on Echo Show devices.

Got a question or suggestion? E-mail us at whoa.labs.for.alexa@gmail.com
